OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FSam Neill's Jurassic Park co-star
OL,7,FLaura Dern has paid tribute to the
OL,8,Factor after his death aged 78, calling
OL,9,Fhim a "true and noble gentleman,
OL,10,Fwrapped up in my dream leading man".
OL,12,FThe Northern Ireland-born New Zealand
OL,13,Factor, best known for playing Dr Alan
OL,14,FGrant in the blockbuster franchise,
OL,15,Fdied in Sydney, Australia, on Monday.
OL,17,FA flood of tributes have poured in for
OL,18,Fthe actor, led by his Jurassic Park co-
OL,19,Fstars including Dern, who played
OL,20,Fpaleobotanist, Ellie Sattler, and Jeff
OL,21,FGoldblum.
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@cO]
