OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FIn a post on Instagram late on Monday,
OL,7,FDern called Neill her "beloved
OL,8,Flifetime friend".
OL,10,FShe said: "He showed me the depths of
OL,11,Floyalty, protectiveness, and love,
OL,12,Falways with the driest of wit.
OL,14,F"He was a true and noble gentleman,
OL,15,Fwrapped up in my dream leading man.
OL,17,F"I will love you forever, Dr. Alan
OL,18,FGrant."
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@PO]rD@KOUvD@AOUyD@AOUzD@GO]
