OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FIn a statement on his production
OL,7,Fcompany Amblin Entertainment's
OL,8,FInstagram page, Jurassic Park director
OL,9,FSteven Spielberg said: "Sam was
OL,10,Fexceptionally collaborative. It was a
OL,11,Fstretch for him to play a character
OL,12,Fwho acted as though children were
OL,13,Fmessy and smelly because this was the
OL,14,Fopposite of the loving father he was
OL,15,Fto his children. I adored making all
OL,16,Fthe Jurassic movies with him.
OL,26,@qD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
