PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784063895
OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,F"Along with Laura Dern and Jeff
OL,7,FGoldblum, we will always have our
OL,8,FJurassic family and Sam will never be
OL,9,Fforgotten by us or his many millions
OL,10,Fof fans around the world."
OL,12,FNeill's Peaky Blinders co-star,
OL,13,FCillian Murphy, described him as "one
OL,14,Fof the finest actors".
OL,16,FHe said: "Like everyone who knew and
OL,17,Fworked with Sam, I admired him and
OL,18,Fadored him in equal measure. He was
OL,19,Fone of the kindest, funniest and
OL,20,Fgentlest people, and one of the finest
OL,21,Factors...RIP."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@ZO]uD@bOUvD@UO]xD@JOU}D@NO]
