OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FNeill played the sadistic, corrupt
OL,7,Fsenior police officer Major Chester
OL,8,FCampbell in the first two seasons of
OL,9,Fthe show, opposite Murphy's notorious
OL,10,Fgang leader Tommy Shelby.
OL,12,FThe show's official page posted a
OL,13,Ftribute on social media which said:
OL,14,F"Sam was one of the key forces that
OL,15,Fgot Peaky Blinders off to a running
OL,16,Fstart, for which we will be forever
OL,17,Fgrateful."
OL,19,FJoe Cole, Neill's co-star in Peaky
OL,20,FBlinders, posted on Instagram: "Rest
OL,21,Fin peace big dog."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@JO]|D@`OU}D@RO]
