OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FFellow New Zealand actor Karl Urban,
OL,7,Fbest known for starring in The Boys,
OL,8,Fcalled Neill "an inspiration for many
OL,9,Fwho followed in his trailblazing
OL,10,Ffootsteps".
OL,12,FDaisy Ridley, who stars with Neill in
OL,13,Fthe as-yet-unreleased film The Last
OL,14,FResort, posted a photo of herself with
OL,15,FNeill on Instagram with several broken
OL,16,Fheart emojis.
OL,26,@pD@NOUrD@JO]
