OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FRufus Sewell, who starred with Neill
OL,7,Fin the 1996 film Victory, posted a
OL,8,Fphoto of them on set at the time and
OL,9,Fwrote: "Lucky to have known him. A
OL,10,Fgreat actor and a lovely man."
OL,12,FNeill's Event Horizon co-star Sean
OL,13,FPertwee said: "Devastated to learn my
OL,14,Ffriend Sam Neill has passed away. A
OL,15,Fsupreme talent, elegant, intelligent,
OL,16,Fhilarious, a truly splendid human.
OL,17,FAlso a major proponent why I married
OL,18,Fmy wife for which I am eternally
OL,19,Fgrateful. Love you Sam."
OL,26,@qD@HOUrD@^O]uD@OOU{D@XO]
