OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FBorn in Omagh, Northern Ireland, to an
OL,7,FEnglish mother and New Zealand father,
OL,8,FNeill first gained attention for his
OL,9,Frole in the 1977 thriller Sleeping
OL,10,FDogs.
OL,12,FHis breakthrough came in Jurassic
OL,13,FPark, a franchise he returned to in
OL,14,FJurassic Park III and 2022's Jurassic
OL,15,FWorld Dominion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784063895
OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FNeill was also widely acclaimed for
OL,7,Fhis turn as New Zealand settler
OL,8,FAlisdair Stewart in Jane Campion's
OL,9,FOscar-winning film The Piano, as well
OL,10,Fas Sean Connery thriller The Hunt For
OL,11,FRed October, and Taika Waititi's
OL,12,Fbreakout hit, Hunt For The
OL,13,FWilderpeople.
OL,15,FHe also found success on television in
OL,16,FThe Tudors, The Simpsons and Alcatraz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
