OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784063895
OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FNew Zealand Prime Minister Christopher
OL,7,FLuxon led tributes to him, writing on
OL,8,FX: "For more than 50 years he took New
OL,9,FZealand stories to the world and his
OL,10,Ftalents helped make our film industry
OL,11,Finto what it is today ` one of our
OL,12,Fgreatest cultural exports. His work
OL,13,Fwill be watched and loved long after
OL,14,Fall of us."
OL,16,FNeill lived on a farm and winery
OL,17,Fcalled Two Paddocks in the Central
OL,18,FOtago region of New Zealand.
OL,26,@pD@DOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
