OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784063895
OL,3,CLaura Dern pays tribute to 'dream
OL,4,Cleading man' Sam Neill
OL,6,FHe established the winery in 1993,
OL,7,Fnext door to his friend, Roger
OL,8,FDonaldson, the director of Sleeping
OL,9,FDogs.
OL,11,FNeill most recently starred in TV
OL,12,Fseries The Twelve, Apples Never Fall
OL,13,Fand Untamed, and two films to be
OL,14,Freleased next year, Godzilla x Kong:
OL,15,FSupernova and The Last Resort.
OL,17,FHe leaves four children and eight
OL,18,Fgrandchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
